<h1 class="hero-h">Fractional CMO Spokane <em style="color:#00C853;font-style:italic;">— senior marketing leadership for operators here.</em></h1>
<p class="hero-sub">Treetop works with B2B mid-market companies in Spokane and across Washington. If you're a founder or CEO between $3M and $30M ARR considering a fractional CMO, here's the Spokane-specific context and engagement model.</p>
<div class="tldr"><div class="tldr-l">Short answer</div><p class="tldr-p">Treetop offers fractional CMO services in Spokane, WA. Engagements run $8K-$25K/month for B2B companies needing senior marketing leadership without a full-time hire. Remote-first with quarterly in-person on-site for Spokane clients when scope warrants.</p></div>
</div></div>

